This is the README file for RTx::WebCronTool, an RT extension providing a
web interface for the built-in "rt-crontool" utility, allowing scheduled
processes to be launched remotely.

Please type "perldoc RTx::WebCronTool" after installation to see the module
usage information.

* Installation

RTx::WebCronTool uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# optional; see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make			# or 'nmake' on Win32
make test
make install

